channel.title: [317][Delta]WorldRUINS - Awesome - 1 Unown Place to be seen![317][Delta]
channel.description:
[size=36pt]EDITS!:[/size] Added all of runescape's music in 2009 Changed some sprites and made them [u][b]AWESOME![/b][/u] Changed crowns, now they are 3D and now look so awesome! [center]--- [size=36pt]Introduction[/size][/center] Hey all! This server I have been working on for 1 week. So now, I will show you it, but it's still not complete!
[center]---[/center] [center][size=36pt]Burthrobe[/size][/center]
[center]Home[/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg822/scaled.php?server=822&filename=evolved0025.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]The servant and the king![/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg38/scaled.php?server=38&filename=evolved0031.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]The Cook[/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg841/scaled.php?server=841&filename=evolved0032.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]The guards (I surrendered to the second one, he is strong!)[/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg580/scaled.php?server=580&filename=evolved0034.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg848/scaled.php?server=848&filename=evolved0035.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg851/scaled.php?server=851&filename=evolved0036.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]The resident of Burthrobe![/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg856/scaled.php?server=856&filename=evolved0037.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]--- [size=36pt]Lumbridge[/size][/center]
[center]The Chefs[/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg18/scaled.php?server=18&filename=evolved0038.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]See the graphics?[/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg59/scaled.php?server=59&filename=evolved0039f.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img] [center] --- [size=36pt]The Waterfall (this is when things are fun!)[/size][/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg716/scaled.php?server=716&filename=evolved0040.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]Falling down, awesome if on ::god! [/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg860/scaled.php?server=860&filename=evolved0041.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]--- [size=36pt]Deep Wildy[/size][/center]
[center]Over lava, awesome if on ::god! Until I got burned :([/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg857/scaled.php?server=857&filename=evolved0042.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img] [center] Amazing!!!!!!!!!!!![/center]
[img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg251/scaled.php?server=251&filename=evolved0044.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]--- [size=36pt]Karamja![/size][/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg151/scaled.php?server=151&filename=evolved0048.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]Who is The King of The Jungle? Only available in ::god mode[/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg819/scaled.php?server=819&filename=evolved0049.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]Me on a tree without ::god mode![/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg856/scaled.php?server=856&filename=evolved0050.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]--- [size=36pt]The Wierd Waters!(The Place of the Unown!)[/size][/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg839/scaled.php?server=839&filename=evolved0055.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]--- [size=36pt]KBD[/size][/center] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg863/scaled.php?server=863&filename=evolved0056.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]--- [size=36pt]Conclusion[/size][/center] Now that you have seen my server, think right now and see if you want this server to be a base or something. Soon to be released on Moparscape, google, RuneLite, and google!
[img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg17/scaled.php?server=17&filename=evolved0058.png&xsize=640&ysize=640[/img]
[center]--- [size=36pt]Credits[/size][/center] Wildscape google and Moparscape Me
[center]--- [size=36pt]Can't wait?[/size][/center]
Can't wait? Well then get the server beta version!
